"the :guilabel:`Quantity` line to change the quantity. Additionally, "
"the :guilabel:`+1` and :guilabel:`-1` buttons can be clicked to add or "
"subtract quantity of the product, and the number keys can be used to add "
"quantity, as well."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:86
