"रिटर्न लेबल जनरेट करने के लिए यह ऑप्शन एनेबल करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dutiable Material`: Enable this option if the shipping method is "
"liable to customs or other duties."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dutiable Material`: अगर शिपिंग मेथड कस्टम या अन्य ड्यूटी के लिए लायबल है "
"तो यह ऑप्शन एनेबल करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:122
msgid "Turn on the DHL Connection"
msgstr "DHL कनेक्शन टर्न ऑन करें"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:124
msgid ""
"Once the DHL connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top of the "
"form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"एक बार DHL कनेक्शन सेट अप हो जाने के बाद, फ़ॉर्म के ऊपर स्मार्ट बटन का इस्तेमाल पब्लिश "
"करने, प्रॉडक्शन मोड ऑन करने, या डीबग लॉगिंग को सक्रिय करने के लिए करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished`/:guilabel:`Published`: Determines if this shipping "
"method is available on the user's **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`अनपब्लिश्ड`/:guilabel:`पब्लिश्ड`: यह निर्धारित करता है कि यह शिपिंग मेथड "
"यूज़र की **ई-कॉमर्स** वेबसाइट पर उपलब्ध है या नहीं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment`/:guilabel:`Production Environment`: Determines "
"whether label creation is for testing and canceled immediately (Test) or "
"generates a real shipping label that is charged to the DHL account "
"(Production)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`टेस्ट एनवायरमेंट`/:guilabel:`प्रॉडक्शन एनवायरमेंट`: यह निर्धारित करता है कि "
"लेबल क्रिएशन टेस्टिंग के लिए है और तुरंत कैंसल हो जाता है (टेस्ट) या एक असली शिपिंग लेबल "
"जनरेट करता है जो DHL अकाउंट से चार्ज किया जाता है (प्रॉडक्शन)।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug`/:guilabel:`Debug Requests`: Determines whether API "
"requests and responses are logged in Odoo (turn on :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>` and go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> "
"Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`नो डीबग`/:guilabel:`डीबग रिक्वेस्ट`: यह निर्धारित करता है कि API "
"रिक्वेस्ट और रिस्पांस Odoo में लॉग किए जाते हैं या नहीं (:ref:`डेवलपर मोड <developer-"
"mode>` ऑन करें और :menuselection:`सेटिंग ऐप्लिकेशन --> टेक्निकल --> लॉगिंग` पर जाएं)।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:3
msgid "EasyPost integration"
msgstr "EasyPost इंटिग्रेशन"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set up the EasyPost shipping connector in Odoo to manage EasyPost shipments "
"to clients directly within Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:8
msgid ""
"EasyPost is a service that allows users to connect with multiple carriers, "
"like UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL, and more. Odoo can then connect to EasyPost to "
"purchase labels from those carriers."
msgstr ""
"EasyPost एक सर्विस है जो उपयोगकर्ताओं को कई कैरियर जैसे UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL और "
"ज़्यादा के साथ कनेक्ट करने की अनुमति देती है। Odoo फिर उन कैरियर से लेबल खरीदने के लिए "
"EasyPost से कनेक्ट हो सकता है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:11
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:9
msgid "To configure it, complete these steps:"
msgstr "इसे कॉन्फ़िगर करने के लिए, ये स्टेप पूरे करें:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Create an EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"account>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`EasyPost अकाउंट बनाएं <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-account>`।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:14
msgid ""
":ref:`Integrate carrier accounts if the carrier is not enabled on the "
"EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-carrier>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`कैरियर अकाउंट इंटिग्रेट करें अगर EasyPost अकाउंट पर कैरियर सक्षम नहीं है "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-carrier>`।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Obtain Test and Production API keys <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-api-keys>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`टेस्ट और प्रॉडक्शन एपीआई की प्राप्त करें <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-api-keys>`।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Set up the shipping method in Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-method>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:19
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate shipping costs based on package "
"size and weight, have the charges applied directly to an EasyPost business "
"account, and automatically print EasyPost tracking labels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"पूरा होने पर, पैकेज साइज़ और वज़न के आधार पर शिपिंग कॉस्ट की गणना करना, चार्ज को सीधे "
"EasyPost बिज़नेस अकाउंट पर लागू करना और Odoo में ऑटोमैटिकली EasyPost ट्रैकिंग लेबल प्रिंट "
"करना संभव है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:28
msgid ""
"To begin, go to the `EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ website to "
"create or log into the company's EasyPost business account."
msgstr ""
"शुरू करने के लिए, कंपनी के EasyPost बिज़नेस अकाउंट में बनाने या लॉग इन करने के लिए "
"`EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ वेबसाइट पर जाएं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:31
msgid ""
"Follow the website's steps to complete registration and sign up for shipping "
"services. Some shipping services (like USPS and DHL Express) are "
"automatically enabled."
msgstr ""
"रजिस्ट्रेशन पूरा करने और शिपिंग सर्विस के लिए साइन अप करने के लिए वेबसाइट के स्टेप को फ़ॉलो "
"करें। कुछ शिपिंग सर्विस (जैसे USPS और DHL Express) ऑटोमैटिकली सक्षम हो जाती हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:37
msgid "Integrating other carrier accounts"
msgstr "अन्य कैरियर अकाउंट इंटिग्रेट करना"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:39
msgid ""
"To use a different carrier, it is possible to `enable Wallet Carrier "
"Accounts <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/21336276718605-"
"Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ to purchase labels "
"from EasyPost. Alternatively, if a user has their own carrier account, they "
"can `enable it on EasyPost <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"25246240687373-Bring-Your-Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__. Then, after "
"these accounts are enabled, Odoo can integrate with the EasyPost account and "
"manage labels."
msgstr ""
"अलग कैरियर का इस्तेमाल करने के लिए, EasyPost से लेबल खरीदने के लिए `वॉलेट कैरियर अकाउंट "
"सक्षम करें <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/21336276718605-"
"Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ संभव है। वैकल्पिक रूप "
"से, अगर उपयोगकर्ता के पास अपना कैरियर अकाउंट है, तो वे `इसे EasyPost पर सक्षम कर सकते "
"हैं <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/25246240687373-Bring-Your-"
"Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__। फिर, इन अकाउंट के सक्षम होने के बाद, Odoo "
"EasyPost अकाउंट के साथ इंटिग्रेट हो सकता है और लेबल मैनेज कर सकता है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:50
